The HTMLCut binary includes compiled Rust crates from crates.io. The complete
dependency graph (~200 packages) is recorded in Cargo.lock. The sections below
cover the licenses and attributions required for binary distribution.

For a full machine-readable license report, run:
  cargo install cargo-about
  cargo about generate about.hbs

